'''天主教阿利瓦爾教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Alivalensis}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Diocese of Aliwal}}）是[[南非|南非]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教開普敦總教區|開普敦總教區]]。

==歷史==
教區的前身是加里普宗座監牧區，於1923年6月12日成立，1936年1月27日升格並易名為阿利瓦爾宗座代牧區。1951年1月11日升為教區。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|date=1951年|volume=43|title=''Suprema Nobis''|page=257|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2043%20%5B1951%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2014-01-22|archive-date=2012-08-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69mL2255U?url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2043%20%5B1951%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==現況==
教區範圍包括[[東開普省|東開普省]]北部，教座位於[[北阿利瓦爾|北阿利瓦爾]]。2012年有教友40,400人（佔轄區總人口7.2%）、兩個堂區、十九名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|若瑟·基齊托 (主教)|Joseph Kizito (Bischof)|若瑟·基齊托}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 15.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/15/191115e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115182806/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/15/191115e.html |archivedate=2019-11-15 |language=en |date=2019-11-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]為{{link-pl|亞當·穆夏韋克|Adam Musiałek|亞當·萊謝克·穆夏韋克}}<ref name="Vatican20170901">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 01.09.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/09/01/170901d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116132010/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/09/01/170901d.html |archivedate=2019-11-16 |language=en |date=2017-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|費德廉·洛賓格爾|Fritz Lobinger}}和{{link-de|彌額爾·韋斯滕貝格|Michael Wüstenberg}}<ref name="Vatican20170901" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 29.04.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/04/29/0207/00655.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116145558/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/04/29/0207/00655.html |archivedate=2019-11-16 |language=it |date=2004-04-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

